l productions have starred tom atkins as rooneycitation needed at steeler games there is a sign that shows a picture of rooney with his characteristic cigar and under the photo the word believecitation needed art rooneys north side golden rule my father always used to tell us boys treat everybody the way youd like to be treated give them the benefit of the doubt but never let anyone mistake kindness for weakness he took the golden rule and put a little bit of the north side in it “ ” — art rooney jr on his father art j rooney was for  years until her  death married to kathleen rooney née mcnulty – kathleen was the mother of arts five sons who are dan rooney the chairman of the board of directors of the pittsburgh steelers and a former united states ambassador to ireland art rooney jr timothy rooney patrick rooney and john rooney all also directors of the pittsburgh steelers she is also grandmother of the couples  grandchildren including current steelers president art rooney ii and us representative thomas j rooney r fl the couple also has about  great grandchildren including actress sisters kate mara and rooney mara referencesedit general klavon jacqueline e rooney arthur joseph the chief bio pennsylvania center for the book retrieved may    specific  a b rooney arthur j jr mchugh roy  ruanaidhthe story of art rooney and his clan artrooneyjrcom pp – isbn    a b johnson vince september   from the pg archives rooney unique in pro football hall of fame pittsburgh postgazette   permanent dead link  art rooney register statistics  history – baseballreferencecom   art rooney   tucker murray screamer the forgotten voice of the pittsburgh steelers isbn   accessdate requires url help  the pittsburgh press – google news archive search    seasons the complete story of the national football league pg   archived copy archived from the original on  retrieved    lawrence journalworld – google news archive search   the pittsburgh press – google news archive search   tuma gary octob